
ZL001 - Fake Microcontroller
Operands
---------
r -> register
v -> value
i -> input [0,1,2,3]
o -> output [0,1,2,3]
l -> lable

maths -> opcode r/v/i r/v/i r/o
ADD
SUB
MUL
DIV

compare -> opcode r/v/i r/v/i
CMP

branching -> opcode l/v/i
BRC
BEQ
BGT
BLT

No operation -> Opcode
NOP

Halt -> Opcode
HLT


IO PORT LOCATION
--------
 ____|0|____
_|         |_
3|  ZL001  |1
_|         |_
 ----|2|----
